<P><DL COMPACT>
<DT>1.
<DD>halyard
<DT>2.
<DD>sheet
<DT>3.
<DD>jib
<DT>4.
<DD>head
</DL>
<BR>____&nbsp;&nbsp;line used to trim a sail
<BR>____&nbsp;&nbsp;toilet
<BR>____&nbsp;&nbsp;line used to hoist and lower a sail
<BR>____&nbsp;&nbsp;triangular sail attached to the forestay of
the foremost mast
</DL>
