<PRE>  &#58;lblbox.This is the label for the box
  This is verbiage for within the box.
  It is formatted normally.
  &#58;elblbox.
</PRE><P><PRE><B>+---This is the label for the box--------------------------------------------+</B></PRE>
This is verbiage for within the box.
It is formatted normally.
