+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+
| &amp;Nt          |    &Ntilde;     | &amp;nt          |    &ntilde;     | &amp;Ntilde      |    &Ntilde;     |
+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+
