+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+
| &amp;plus        |    &#43;     | &amp;plusend     |    &#43;     | &amp;plusmin     |    &plusmn;     |
+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+
| &amp;plusmn      |    &plusmn;     | &amp;plusop      |    &#43;     | &amp;pm          |    &plusmn;     |
+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+
