+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+
| &amp;rbrc        |    &#125;     | &amp;rbrk        |    &#93;     | &amp;rdarrow     |    &#61;&gt;    |
+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+
| &amp;reg         |    &reg;     | &amp;regtm       |    &reg;     | &amp;rpar        |    &#41;     |
+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+
| &amp;rparen      |    &#41;     | &amp;sdq         |    &quot;     | &amp;sect        |    &sect;     |
+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+
| &amp;section     |    &sect;     | &amp;semi        |    &#59;     | &amp;shy         |    &shy;     |
+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+
