+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+
| &amp;ssbl        |    &nbsp;     | &amp;ssq         |    &#39;     | &amp;STAR        |    &#42;     |
+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+
| &amp;sub0        |    <SUB>0</SUB>     | &amp;sub1        |    <SUB>1</SUB>     | &amp;sub2        |    <SUB>2</SUB>     |
+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+--------------+----------+
