<PRE><TT>
+============+=====+=================================+=======================+
| Tag        | How | Comments (fully supported       | Related B2H options   |
|            |  ?  | unless specified otherwise)     |                       |
+============+=====+=================================+=======================+
| &#58;ABBREV.   |  I  | Attributes supported: ID=       | DEFTEXT=              |
|            |     |                                 | DEFTEXT.ABBREV= )     |
