|            |     | REFID=                          | DEFTEXT.QANSREF= )    |
+------------+-----+---------------------------------+-----------------------+
| &#58;ANSWER    |  I  | Attributes supported: REFID=    |                       |
|            |     | See also 5.11, "Question and    |                       |
|            |     | Answer tags"                    |                       |
+------------+-----+---------------------------------+-----------------------+
