|            |     | ORESP= , PRESP= , PROBD= ,      | HRTAG= SETUPTAG=      |
|            |     | REFID= SCALE= , SEVERITY= ,     |                       |
|            |     | SPRESP= , STYLE= , SYSACT= ,    |                       |
|            |     | URESP= and XPL=                 |                       |
|            |     | STYLE=RULE causes the value     |                       |
|            |     | specified for the HRTAG.4=      |                       |
|            |     | option (normally a &lt;HR&gt; ) to be |                       |
|            |     | inserted around each &#58;CODE.     |                       |
|            |     | block.                          |                       |
