|            |     | EXPAND , REFID= and SCALE=      |                       |
|            |     | Implemented using a monospaced  |                       |
|            |     | font on a line 78 characters    |                       |
|            |     | wide.                           |                       |
+------------+-----+---------------------------------+-----------------------+
| &#58;DIRHDR.   |  I  |                                 |                       |
+------------+-----+---------------------------------+-----------------------+
