|            |     | , SHADE= and WIDTH=PAGE         | FIGCAPLOC= HRTAG=     |
|            |     | When generating HTML 2: if      | SETUPTAG= and SHADE=  |
|            |     | FRAME=NONE , the figure is      |                       |
|            |     | preceded and followed by a      |                       |
|            |     | blank line, otherwise the       |                       |
|            |     | figure is preceded and followed |                       |
|            |     | by the value specified for the  |                       |
|            |     | HRTAG.2= option (normally &lt;HR&gt;  |                       |
|            |     | ).                              |                       |
|            |     | When generating HTML 3 or       |                       |
|            |     | higher: the figure is enclosed  |                       |
|            |     | within a single-row,            |                       |
|            |     | single-cell table (with BORDER  |                       |
|            |     | turned on if FRAME=NONE is <I>not</I>  |                       |
|            |     | specified)                      |                       |
