|            |     | CIX2= ... CIX9= , ID= , SEE=    |                       |
|            |     | and SEEID=                      |                       |
+------------+-----+---------------------------------+-----------------------+
| &#58;IH2.      |  I  | Attributes supported: ID= ,     |                       |
|            |     | REFID= , SEE= and SEEID=        |                       |
+------------+-----+---------------------------------+-----------------------+
| &#58;IH3.      |  I  | Attributes supported: ID= and   | INDEXREFLINK=DEFTEXT= |
|            |     | REFID=                          | (                     |
|            |     |                                 | DEFTEXT.INDEXENTRYL=  |
|            |     |                                 | and                   |
|            |     |                                 | DEFTEXT.INDEXENTRYR=  |
|            |     |                                 | )                     |
+------------+-----+---------------------------------+-----------------------+
| &#58;I1.       |  I  | Attributes supported: CIX1= ,   |                       |
|            |     | CIX2= ... CIX9= , ID= and PG= ( |                       |
|            |     | PG=END causes the tag to be     |                       |
|            |     | ignored).                       |                       |
+------------+-----+---------------------------------+-----------------------+
| &#58;I2.-&#58;I3.  |  I  | Attributes supported: ID= , PG= | INDEXREFLINK=DEFTEXT= |
|            |     | ( PG=END causes the tag to be   | (                     |
|            |     | ignored) and REFID= .           | DEFTEXT.INDEXENTRYL=  |
|            |     |                                 | and                   |
|            |     |                                 | DEFTEXT.INDEXENTRYR=  |
|            |     |                                 | )                     |
+------------+-----+---------------------------------+-----------------------+
| &#58;IBMLPS.   |  I  | Attributes supported: COPYR=    |                       |
|            |     | and SEC=                        |                       |
+------------+-----+---------------------------------+-----------------------+
| &#58;INDEX.    |  I  | Attributes supported: ID=       | DEFTEXT=              |
|            |     |                                 | DEFTEXT.INDEX<VAR>xxx</VAR>= ),  |
|            |     |                                 | INDEX= INDEXTAG=      |
|            |     |                                 | INDEXTOC=             |
|            |     |                                 | INDEXTOCTAG=          |
+------------+-----+---------------------------------+-----------------------+
| &#58;IREF.     |  I  | Attributes supported: PG= (     |                       |
|            |     | PG=END causes the tag to be     |                       |
|            |     | ignored) and REFID=             |                       |
+------------+-----+---------------------------------+-----------------------+
| &#58;KWD.      |  I  | Attributes supported: DEF , OPT |                       |
|            |     | and REQ                         |                       |
+------------+-----+---------------------------------+-----------------------+
| &#58;L.        |  I  | Attributes supported: LID=      |                       |
|            |     | See 5.12, "Interdocument        |                       |
|            |     | linking (BookManager tags)"     |                       |
+------------+-----+---------------------------------+-----------------------+
| &#58;LBLBOX.   |  I  | If generating HTML 2 output,    | BORDERTAG=,           |
|            |     | the width of the box header and | LINEWIDTH= SETUPTAG=  |
|            |     | trailer line is defined by the  |                       |
|            |     | value of the LINEWIDTH= option  |                       |
|            |     | For HTML 3 or higher, a         |                       |
|            |     | single-cell, two-row table is   |                       |
|            |     | generated.                      |                       |
+------------+-----+---------------------------------+-----------------------+
| &#58;LDESC.    |  I  | Attributes supported: DOCID= ,  | DOCDESC=              |
|            |     | OBJECT= and OBJTYPE=            |                       |
|            |     | For the OBJTYPE= attribute, the |                       |
|            |     | HEAD , BOOK , FIG , TABLE and   |                       |
|            |     | SPOT values are supported; all  |                       |
|            |     | others are ignored.             |                       |
|            |     | The DOCID= attribute points to  |                       |
|            |     | the B2H DOCDESC= <I>option</I>, not    |                       |
|            |     | the &#58;DOCDESC <I>tag</I>. See 5.12,     |                       |
|            |     | "Interdocument linking          |                       |
|            |     | (BookManager tags)"             |                       |
