</STRONG></TD></TR></TABLE><BR><STRONG>Explanation&#58; </STRONG>The <TT>&#58;SCHEDULE</TT> tag referenced by
<TT>&#58;SCHDATE</TT> was not physically defined before the
<TT>&#58;SCHDATE</TT> tag was encountered.
<BR><STRONG>Severity&#58; </STRONG>Warning (RC set to 4)
<P><TABLE><TR><TD VALIGN="TOP"><STRONG>B2H418</STRONG></TD><TD><STRONG>Out-of-sequence <TT>&#46;CONFIG</TT>
