improperly nested
<BR><STRONG>Severity&#58; </STRONG>Error (RC set to 8)
<P><TABLE><TR><TD VALIGN="TOP"><STRONG>B2H431</STRONG></TD><TD><STRONG>Number of columns not specified! Assuming <TT>COLS='*'</TT>.
</STRONG></TD></TR></TABLE><BR><STRONG>Explanation&#58; </STRONG>A tag (or the referenced definition tag) does not specify the
